snippet.title: Mega Drive Longplay [411] Pink goes to Hollywood
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Mad-Matt

Boring plat former.  No real story to play through.  Just go through each level until you have played them all with no real ending.  Some levels stand out graphically more than others with the best gfx shown on levels that have a much larger scale than yourself. -
